      "value": "**Directionality convention:**\n`sourceInstanceId` is the asserting instance; `targetInstanceId` is the related instance. The Relation reads: \"source [relationType] target.\""
    },
    {
      "fieldId": "1a000026-0000-4000-a000-000000000026",
      "value": "This convention must be consistent across implementations. See Invariant 16."
